{"tid":293723,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"FreeStyle結束營運","createTime":"2017-06-22T11:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T03:39:11.000Z","uid":2863,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c5fff34416e6f3d1fc99070736d641a04328a68","tid":293723,"uid":2863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:40:32.000Z","msg":"致所有Free style的玩家們：<br />\n　　今天，小編向大家宣布一個沉痛的消息。Free Style伺服器將於7月31日關閉伺服器，在此遊戲也必需告一個段落。<br />\nFree Style在紅心辣椒結束了從2006年至2017年逾十年的代理，其中經歷了大大小小的項目更新及改版。 <br />\nFree Style是一款人物素質、裝備、投球命中計算等都非常複雜的遊戲，不管在營運活動設計、測試人員、伺服器管理等方面，<br />\n都需要比其他遊戲投入更多的人力支援。小編亦非常不捨與玩家們告別。<br />\n　　我們了解再多安慰的話語，都無法抹滅對於喜愛Free Style的玩家，所造成成的傷害。<br />\n身為台灣休閒遊戲專業紅心辣椒，我們想著最後還可以為Free style的玩家做些什麼，可以讓Free style的玩家享受遊戲到最後一刻。<br />\n最後的免費萬元積點歡樂送、一代精神 二代傳承活動<br />\n　　感謝大家從2006年紅心辣椒代理Free Style以來對於遊戲的支持，但請相信，我們一樣不捨結束Free Style。<br />\n在未來，畫面表現、音樂、音效展現，遊戲玩法更加突出的Free Style 2 相信也可以獲得玩家的青睞。<br />\n小編還會繼續在Free Style2為大家服務，最後跟所有珍愛Free Style的玩家說道「珍重再見」。<br />\n小編也會在粉絲團或其他活動與大家互動，謝謝大家。<br />\n<br />\n雖然係FB比人屌到仆街19號完儲值活動就公告話關SER<br />\n不過呢隻驚真係好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中學雞果陣已經玩緊<br />\n由數碼戲胞執柒左之後由黑心辣椒再開係有啲開心<br />\n但佢自從由技術GAME<br />\n得分同控球既反跑三分<br />\n小前中距離同上籃技巧<br />\n大前鋒高彈跳值係罰球線起跳令人防不勝防<br />\n中鋒秒板，可以卡位卡到對方搶唔到板等等..<br />\n不過隻Game最尾都係屈點裝，合分流合到1LV要同45LV打<br />\n已經係技術補救唔到..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗚啊..仲有一個月就執啦<br />\n我隻絕版KARA角具荷拉啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係咁多個最得意架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd401730d9598e105b899e829fa98e37c728f79","tid":293723,"uid":1020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:44:38.000Z","msg":"隻GAME冇外掛就好玩"},{"pid":"9d3eb3a3f57c09b8beb02790c4c50f3eab342942","tid":293723,"uid":2863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"雖然我而家玩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外掛呢啲都不在話下<br />\n角色多，衫多，技都好多<br />\n不過黑心辣椒玩到技能都要儲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話某啲技係要點數買都仲合理<br />\n但乜鳩都充值真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩到後期直情連商店果啲衫都冇永久買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142949f1c8f4320d8b0365309244e48dde96e472","tid":293723,"uid":105552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:13:03.000Z","msg":"依隻驚陪左我6年中學時光<br />\n最尾因為外掛太多棄撚左<br />\n個陣你根本唔知佢係咪開緊外掛<br />\n事關好多都小開 改到110 120<br />\n不過隻驚捱到依家算係咁"},{"pid":"7188a1008996d4a1ab75b8d338a5ab4c8660b9e2","tid":293723,"uid":2863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:20:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依隻驚陪左我6年中學時光<br />\n最尾因為外掛太多棄撚左<br />\n個陣你根本唔知佢係咪開緊外掛<br />\n事關好多都小開 改到110 120<br />\n不過隻驚捱到依家算係咁</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真，改得唔洗多<br />\n買D假飾品改到同儲點裝差唔多已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢果陣髮衫褲鞋各+15<br />\n仲要3件飾品<br />\n1LV都可以秒板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2820568db0d02966da593b9f30f2f9531b4a5dd","tid":293723,"uid":15490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"當年玩得好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cec0ff1c5cfeb5caf486288da55e51264b23be","tid":293723,"uid":12055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:24:53.000Z","msg":"中學最愛"},{"pid":"4a7b8d53a57f8c9756472b9b480ec23da3f4206e","tid":293723,"uid":64899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:06:35.000Z","msg":"果時話07年尾出55全場，之後唔知出左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166e1d8e1d4fe5ea90bf610226b12c8041510647","tid":293723,"uid":124414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:08:18.000Z","msg":"Freestyle2 好撚on9 , C 同PF 射3分仲準過外線"},{"pid":"ff3a8a09484776798466699bc0b6e26f84b974a4","tid":293723,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:09:55.000Z","msg":"我淨係知隻game排一場仲耐過玩既時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4b97a346cdadb3c846a70d8613ee19dac63b58","tid":293723,"uid":2863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果時話07年尾出55全場，之後唔知出左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似之前話整過<br />\n但當年既網速玩係LAG到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最尾都係變返33GAME"},{"pid":"a02615e0ec4cb178332a1d08de2755947cff9569","tid":293723,"uid":2863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:56:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Freestyle2 好撚on9 , C 同PF 射3分仲準過外線</blockquote><br />\n見到啲公仔都唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2784157c9dc5f33e81ad0f975defb088aeef646","tid":293723,"uid":2863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我淨係知隻game排一場仲耐過玩既時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家個版本真係排勁耐先Load到一場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93397e084790481b2fb6ee9a8e127ae3693c62f1","tid":293723,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"讀書個陣成日玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊玩個同學都無聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c3bd7eb4ede5e1cfcec06407a7b698829bb348","tid":293723,"uid":2863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀書個陣成日玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊玩個同學都無聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無啦<br />\n要玩真係得返呢個月..之後唔會有得再玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}